translated: Hultqvist, Gustaf Abraham, postmaster, Vetlanda, born on July 28th, 1883 in Gällaryd, Jönköping County. Son of the primary school teacher Alfred H. and Elise Nilsson. Married Karin Lundberg in 1916. They had three children: Lars-Gösta, born 1917, Birgit Sofia, born 1918, and Bengt Abraham, born 1920. Started working for the postal service in Jönköping in 1904. Worked as a postal clerk in different locations before becoming a postmaster in Vetlanda in 1942. Information about his military service was not provided.
